---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="can’t focus? here’s how to fix it naturally"
  description="if your attention feels scattered or weak, learn what causes it and how to restore focus through simple rhythm changes."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">guide</p>
      <h1>can’t focus? here’s what’s causing it</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        if your attention feels scattered or weak, it’s usually not a discipline issue — it’s overstimulation and unstable rhythms.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        fix the inputs and rhythm, and focus starts to come back.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>common causes</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>constant phone and media use</p>
          <p>poor sleep quality</p>
          <p>lack of sunlight</p>
          <p>too many inputs at once</p>
          <p>no mental stillness</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what’s happening</h2>
        <p>
          your brain adapts to stimulation. when it’s constantly fed fast, high-intensity input,
          normal tasks feel slow and difficult.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section accent-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>quick reset</h2>
      <div class="content-block">
        <p>reduce short-form content</p>
        <p>focus on one task at a time</p>
        <p>get better sleep</p>
        <p>spend time in quiet environments</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">focus</span>
        </div>
        <h2>reduce stimulation</h2>
        <p>
          blue light blocking glasses can help reduce overstimulation from screens and support clearer focus.
        </p>
        <a href="/recommendations/blue-light-glasses" class="button">view recommended option</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">nervous system</span>
        </div>
        <h2>support calm focus</h2>
        <p>
          magnesium can help support nervous system balance, which may improve attention and mental clarity.
        </p>
        <a href="/recommendations/magnesium" class="button">view recommended option</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">related</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">system</span>
        </div>
        <h2>go deeper</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p><a href="/brain-fog">clear brain fog</a></p>
          <p><a href="/why-you-feel-tired-all-the-time">fix low energy</a></p>
          <p><a href="/how-to-fix-sleep">fix sleep first</a></p>
          <p><a href="/start-here">understand the full system</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>